TylesBase Installation Instructions.
====================================

Let <tylesBase> refer to the source directory. 

1. Make sure the following prerequisites are installed:

   ocaml
   findlib
   ocamldsort
   extLib

2. Change to the <tylesBase> directory

   cd <tylesBase>

3. To compile, type

   make all

   This will generate the files tylesBase.cm{i,a,xa}. These will be
   under the _build/src directory, and you can link to them there.

4. To make the documentation, type

   make doc

   This produces documentation in html format. The root is
   doc/html/index.html.

5. If needed, you can delete all automatically generated files by
   typing
   
   make clean
